{"tid":1320231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭邦仲: 關於「民意逆轉」 呢篇文一定要推!!","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T09:17:52.000Z","uid":1393,"like":264,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb61a281af5acde2912fac00e6f9ba5e6a1c86c","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:43:35.000Z","msg":"首先，民意逆轉是存在的，<br />\n問題是我們很多時候，<br />\n卻經常誤會了民意的表達方式。<br />\n我可以肯定在近日，<br />\n於社會一般民意上，<br />\n必然會多了很多「警察也是人」的說法。<br />\n這會使部份示威者感到所謂的「民意逆轉」，<br />\n很多人會開始想要急著為抗爭者暴力的行為辯護，<br />\n什至有想要使市民更同情抗爭者的想法。<br />\n而我認為，這並沒有必要，<br />\n我們需要理解到的是，<br />\n民意的表現很多時候不是直觀的。<br />\n關鍵是你能否找出埋藏在背後的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這裡，<br />\n也要談及到華人社會的價值觀的問題。<br />\n首先問題是，<br />\n一般非既得利益者和被欺壓的市民，<br />\n為什麼其立場多數依然是支持政府？<br />\n其答案是因為「恐懼」。<br />\n他們之所以支持政府，<br />\n並不是因為真心或洗腦與否，<br />\n因而對它的壞處視而不見。<br />\n恰好相反，<br />\n它們正正是因為了解極權的暴虐，<br />\n從而感到恐懼而被迫支持政府，<br />\n幻想自己與極權站在同一陣線，<br />\n以增加自己的安全感，<br />\n這是我們經常會說的威權統治。<br />\n也是我們長久以來，<br />\n都把政治當成是天災的結果。<br />\n天災是不可回避的，<br />\n常人只能敬拜它祈求風調雨順，<br />\n所以嚴格來說，大多數支持暴政的觀點，<br />\n並不是一種立場，而是一種國民信仰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後請回想一下，<br />\n在示威者被警察毆打時，<br />\n我們沒有看到支持政府的人會可憐示威者，<br />\n反而說男殺女姦打得好。<br />\n然後，當漸漸有些示威者開始反擊時，<br />\n這些人會痛罵抗爭者，<br />\n說他們禽獸不如，簡直無法無天。<br />\n到了最近，當多數示威者都開始武裝自己，<br />\n為武力抗爭做準備，並打傷了不少警察時，<br />\n社會上卻漸漸多了「警察很可憐、警察也是人」的言論。<br />\n這整個過程，才是真正的民意逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民意逆轉了的部份，<br />\n並不是指一般人立場的轉變，<br />\n而是代表了，<br />\n他們之所以說警察可憐，<br />\n最大的主因並不是因為他們支持警察，<br />\n而是他們對於政權的信仰和警察的恐懼感降低。<br />\n市民開始感覺到，<br />\n政府威權統治的天秤已開始失衡，<br />\n並向著示威者的方向慢慢傾斜。<br />\n經過這兩個月的洗禮後，<br />\n一般人開始發現到，演化到這個狀況，<br />\n警察和政府已經沒有能力完全消滅示威者，<br />\n也沒有辦法使香港回到往日的生活。<br />\n然而在現時示威者的人數、經濟及動員能力下，<br />\n開罪示威者所要負擔的成本，<br />\n比起開罪政府和警察還要更高。<br />\n如果反對示威者，<br />\n就會如同吉野家般成為眾矢之的，<br />\n而公開支持政府和警察，<br />\n卻沒有人會為他們的利益作任何保障。<br />\n這種種的因素，<br />\n將會使本來對抗爭者的窮追猛打開始軟化，<br />\n由拳頭大就是正義的嘲笑，<br />\n變為了動之以情的訴諸同理心，<br />\n由本來見風使盡𢃇的助紂為虐，<br />\n變為了受害者式的示弱。<br />\n什至連底層的警員，<br />\n也開始會把矛頭指向高官而非示威者，<br />\n因為他們知道，示威者的力量過於強大，<br />\n他們無法消滅示威者，<br />\n只能選擇對付另一個更好欺負的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n我認為對於現在的示威者來說，<br />\n他們並不需要可憐或同情。<br />\n他們更需要的，<br />\n是公眾表揚和保護敢於勇武抗爭的人，<br />\n突顯他們已擁有與警察同等、<br />\n什至以上的民間武力及支援，<br />\n並且同時擁有施以經濟制裁的強大市場。<br />\n誰敢無故攻擊示威者的話，<br />\n就會被施以報復打擊，這才是最重要的。<br />\n不需要消耗太多時間進行辯論，<br />\n因為這沒有結果。<br />\n太在乎綿羊的想法不會為你帶來任何收獲，<br />\n因為綿羊本來就沒有想法。<br />\n他們追求的不是任何的主張或理念，而是安全感。<br />\n當他們對示威者的敬畏大於政府時，<br />\n那麼對權威感的服從，<br />\n自然會驅使他們找出理據去支持示威者的行為，<br />\n就如同他們當初無容置疑地支持極權政府一樣。"},{"pid":"14e8383f4c0df4cc328d312c2121593ef062939d","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"補返LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10218646727695837&amp;id=1127162543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10218646727695837%26id%3D1127162543&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=345dbe50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10218646727695837&amp;id=1127162543</a>"},{"pid":"88a25b90985c75868af2fdd2480601721a827c43","tid":1320231,"uid":35430,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"我一直都係咁睇華人社會<br />\n根本華人係患有先天性精神病"},{"pid":"7d2ea9dea5af59287cfb5b7c33866630fe28350a","tid":1320231,"uid":862,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"推高汁"},{"pid":"af870a1976bc7f4e3d3a090a585fa71f04368846","tid":1320231,"uid":44358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毅進犬，你打死市民等坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n市民比你砌生豬肉，最多去歐洲申請政治庇護咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09012f02bea1b26c5c088ccd88d5d626afdac108","tid":1320231,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb383c81a533c7531cfb77679a35df0134bfe72","tid":1320231,"uid":191487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"推，精華"},{"pid":"6f90ec9e545026791a0f75a5700b96e850cac539","tid":1320231,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"同我諗既差唔多<br />\n華人社會中間派既就係低智商牆頭草既生物<br />\n所以先叫做逆五毛文宣 大家鬥洗腦"},{"pid":"fa62b0b918e1d636ef790b578cd180cf9a044a99","tid":1320231,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ab5133e26358eae04fc44797f1d068661ae1439","tid":1320231,"uid":104917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"邊個拳頭硬邊個就有道理<br />\n對於佢地嚟講係咁"},{"pid":"c1080a8b38fa31e32ce69d08fcefa59e2a769cf2","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"我地已經冇得揀，冇退路，一退就會墮入萬丈深淵永不超生。「共犯」越多，越強大，我地越安全！<br />\n<br />\n721大家裝備自己，同我行出嚟！"},{"pid":"3659e16c78e495b05386d64e8679d8fb40f46830","tid":1320231,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"8a22ca27ee4149b3a20bdb82cdbe4f8cd36dc0c7","tid":1320231,"uid":254594,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"其實民意逆轉重要性係講緊同路人既民意風向<br />\n簡單講，亦即係相同立場既人 對勇武抗爭既容納度<br />\n如果武力好似黑警咁一下子升到最高級別，好容易會被同路人唾棄<br />\n舉個例 有班極端份子提議搞暗殺，我諗99%同路人會阻止或割蓆，因為大家接受程度唔會一下子提高<br />\n但如果係由對家首先提升，我地處被動位置，示威者不得不作出防禦及反制，同理心作崇下先至可以得到最大認同及持久性"},{"pid":"1f8a15fe646ec49e80fe36b8295dc3a03fc72716","tid":1320231,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99475f0724afd9efa27d174a6de1b67b2082017f","tid":1320231,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"即係勝利球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b31711cabd857c174891eebe18993b69f064fb0","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"正如孫中山搞緊革命時99%清朝人都會反對。"},{"pid":"c208cc1ea98abb759e232a28505b0d6aa6bd0817","tid":1320231,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"好似睇到好透咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b1bbbe12ece7d6a193e294029e75925ac445ab","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"b782e16839e96e0639870683dbcb5841a1eb3eba","tid":1320231,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">清君側，靖內難</span></span>"},{"pid":"63f156c3376c87b6e33607321b7c4fc6bbfb3cd6","tid":1320231,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgVpzV3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgVpzV3.png&h=6d1a1e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCAwZnJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCAwZnJ.png&h=a1113ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ij5wZnJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fij5wZnJ.png&h=e75de421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e42f79062179e0ae7a249cdf606d50d6587ed8a2","tid":1320231,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"何來逆轉?  民意只是唔支持暴力，但不會支持共產黨。"},{"pid":"db0a9d452eb1aad62fe620838528ad782ac494d0","tid":1320231,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcd6565ca0228747881746d68b1bd555aec63d93","tid":1320231,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"講得好中"},{"pid":"808ba466b7249f2f07c4b4dc4293c3a29f9d94e8","tid":1320231,"uid":3782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:41:47.000Z","msg":"高汁<br />\n勝利球迷佔多數 睇到唔對路轉駄既人先係最多"},{"pid":"9ab6cf9ea3f6565669d3e6944ebc4d84dbdac0d2","tid":1320231,"uid":17379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bb61a281af5acde2912fac00e6f9ba5e6a1c86c","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:43:35.000Z","msg":"首先，民意逆轉是存在的，<br />\n問題是我們很多時候，<br />\n卻經常誤會了民意的表達方式。<br />\n我可以肯定在近日，<br />\n於社會一般民意上，<br />\n必然會多了很多「警察也是人」的說法。<br />\n這會使部份示威者感到所謂的「民意逆轉」，<br />\n很多人會開始想要急著為抗爭者暴力的行為辯護，<br />\n什至有想要使市民更同情抗爭者的想法。<br />\n而我認為，這並沒有必要，<br />\n我們需要理解到的是，<br />\n民意的表現很多時候不是直觀的。<br />\n關鍵是你能否找出埋藏在背後的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這裡，<br />\n也要談及到華人社會的價值觀的問題。<br />\n首先問題是，<br />\n一般非既得利益者和被欺壓的市民，<br />\n為什麼其立場多數依然是支持政府？<br />\n其答案是因為「恐懼」。<br />\n他們之所以支持政府，<br />\n並不是因為真心或洗腦與否，<br />\n因而對它的壞處視而不見。<br />\n恰好相反，<br />\n它們正正是因為了解極權的暴虐，<br />\n從而感到恐懼而被迫支持政府，<br />\n幻想自己與極權站在同一陣線，<br />\n以增加自己的安全感，<br />\n這是我們經常會說的威權統治。<br />\n也是我們長久以來，<br />\n都把政治當成是天災的結果。<br />\n天災是不可回避的，<br />\n常人只能敬拜它祈求風調雨順，<br />\n所以嚴格來說，大多數支持暴政的觀點，<br />\n並不是一種立場，而是一種國民信仰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後請回想一下，<br />\n在示威者被警察毆打時，<br />\n我們沒有看到支持政府的人會可憐示威者，<br />\n反而說男殺女姦打得好。<br />\n然後，當漸漸有些示威者開始反擊時，<br />\n這些人會痛罵抗爭者，<br />\n說他們禽獸不如，簡直無法無天。<br />\n到了最近，當多數示威者都開始武裝自己，<br />\n為武力抗爭做準備，並打傷了不少警察時，<br />\n社會上卻漸漸多了「警察很可憐、警察也是人」的言論。<br />\n這整個過程，才是真正的民意逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民意逆轉了的部份，<br />\n並不是指一般人立場的轉變，<br />\n而是代表了，<br />\n他們之所以說警察可憐，<br />\n最大的主因並不是因為他們支持警察，<br />\n而是他們對於政權的信仰和警察的恐懼感降低。<br />\n市民開始感覺到，<br />\n政府威權統治的天秤已開始失衡，<br />\n並向著示威者的方向慢慢傾斜。<br />\n經過這兩個月的洗禮後，<br />\n一般人開始發現到，演化到這個狀況，<br />\n警察和政府已經沒有能力完全消滅示威者，<br />\n也沒有辦法使香港回到往日的生活。<br />\n然而在現時示威者的人數、經濟及動員能力下，<br />\n開罪示威者所要負擔的成本，<br />\n比起開罪政府和警察還要更高。<br />\n如果反對示威者，<br />\n就會如同吉野家般成為眾矢之的，<br />\n而公開支持政府和警察，<br />\n卻沒有人會為他們的利益作任何保障。<br />\n這種種的因素，<br />\n將會使本來對抗爭者的窮追猛打開始軟化，<br />\n由拳頭大就是正義的嘲笑，<br />\n變為了動之以情的訴諸同理心，<br />\n由本來見風使盡𢃇的助紂為虐，<br />\n變為了受害者式的示弱。<br />\n什至連底層的警員，<br />\n也開始會把矛頭指向高官而非示威者，<br />\n因為他們知道，示威者的力量過於強大，<br />\n他們無法消滅示威者，<br />\n只能選擇對付另一個更好欺負的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n我認為對於現在的示威者來說，<br />\n他們並不需要可憐或同情。<br />\n他們更需要的，<br />\n是公眾表揚和保護敢於勇武抗爭的人，<br />\n突顯他們已擁有與警察同等、<br />\n什至以上的民間武力及支援，<br />\n並且同時擁有施以經濟制裁的強大市場。<br />\n誰敢無故攻擊示威者的話，<br />\n就會被施以報復打擊，這才是最重要的。<br />\n不需要消耗太多時間進行辯論，<br />\n因為這沒有結果。<br />\n太在乎綿羊的想法不會為你帶來任何收獲，<br />\n因為綿羊本來就沒有想法。<br />\n他們追求的不是任何的主張或理念，而是安全感。<br />\n當他們對示威者的敬畏大於政府時，<br />\n那麼對權威感的服從，<br />\n自然會驅使他們找出理據去支持示威者的行為，<br />\n就如同他們當初無容置疑地支持極權政府一樣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"所以我就諗其實21號出到去 要做啲咩先會有真普選 唔好講咩對抗黑警就會有 假如 真係入多次垃圾會 係咪有人就讀普選宣言 下次選舉會有真普選 大家focus好似仲定咗係點用武去抗暴 但係較少諗遠少少 要做啲咩先會行到真普選呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc051ed785aaf764bb1558f7ef3435ff82edb08","tid":1320231,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9c04e185ec40672c28c63e906edcfb2d7a6713d","tid":1320231,"uid":109775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9034621da282b892176e79a4c749c556f67c398","tid":1320231,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:50:04.000Z","msg":"好反映到身邊嘅民意"},{"pid":"a1981f540dd213e5b99eb5f020d284571fee603e","tid":1320231,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:50:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ec579042bb8d0a623a903c774fe4e9aad2e93e0d","tid":1320231,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明白，文宣轉向<br />\n本土價值，勇武捍衛<br />\n時代革命，光復香港"},{"pid":"962b40139454567c78e33bb13cfc4d0e5a2f03c9","tid":1320231,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a25b90985c75868af2fdd2480601721a827c43","tid":1320231,"uid":35430,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"我一直都係咁睇華人社會<br />\n根本華人係患有先天性精神病"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"動物天性"},{"pid":"4bc87717ea11e2b3f1205422cf5958bfb5f8c7cf","tid":1320231,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8903cf0af6424ee75374173b14333f4090f1c2","tid":1320231,"uid":108692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ab4235031b3b4b98f376973253d9b78d917586a","tid":1320231,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"546167b0bf22a56a1aad9fed52626ace1cb78214","tid":1320231,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d9a3f54a9c6878a8c63bff8ba027e98fe71b37","tid":1320231,"uid":23951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"根本華人的DNA就係Glory Hunter，睇返民國丶二戰的歷史就知"},{"pid":"b5fefe1044dc63109a3bb0c0f5021aa7da14794b","tid":1320231,"uid":116785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"文宣手足值得一睇"},{"pid":"265b6d6769fa94cd78f1411e9680e3685805de8a","tid":1320231,"uid":28435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話民意係勝利球迷，睇七一衝玻璃由鬼變死士就知"},{"pid":"24ce80bb53316aeb953046f8177a45172a022617","tid":1320231,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"第一次聽到咁嘅講法，又好似幾有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"